Lorentzian Causal Diamond Verification Scripts

This software implements and verifies the novel geometric and algebraic 
concepts presented in the paper:
> Yannick Schmitt. (2026). Exact Discretisation and Boundary Observables in Lorentzian Causal Diamonds. Zenodo. https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19338306

Specifically, this includes the numerical verification of:
- The ternary Minkowski lattice L and lightlike vector enumeration.
- The 21 order-4 plaquette structure and incidence matrix.
- The exact integer spectrum of the 12x12 Plaquette Laplacian.
- The leading-order partition function and specific-heat peak (beta_c ≈ 2.7364).

If you use this code or the implemented algorithms in your research, 
please cite the paper mentioned above.
